column5: Well I had Long Shank from Nuatrik Charters join me yesterday for some good old Cat fishing on the Grand ..it was a beauty day to be on the water the fishing was not fast and furious but the laughs and good chats made for a awesome day ...must have had 40 bites  but only a few good fish landed ..Thanks for joining me Werner ...Fishmaster
Nice goin Werner!!..  ..Now get back to riggin that boat of yers so we can go Salmon fishin.....
